<h4 style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 18px;">This website uses Google Adwords</h4>
<p>This website uses the Google AdWords remarketing and customer match services to exclude advertising on third party websites (including Google) to previous site visitors or site users.
It could mean that we EXCLUDE advertisements to previous visitors on our site. This could be in the form of excluding an advertisement on the Google search results page or a site in the Google Display Network. Third-party vendors, including Google, use cookies to serve or exclude ads based on someone’s past visits to this website. Of course, any data collected will be used in accordance with our own privacy policy and Google’s privacy policy.
It could also mean that we EXCLUDE advertisements to previous applicants that have submitted their email address to us for the purpose of obtaining or using or services offered on our websites
AdWords remarketing will allow us to not display ads to you based on what parts of this website you have viewed by placing a cookie on your machine or not display ads if you are logged in to any google services by using your email address to exclude advertisements to you using the Google Adwords customer match service.</p>

<h4 style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 18px;">This cookie does not in anyway identify you or give access to your computer.</h4>
<p>Google AdWords Remarketing allows us to tailor our marketing to better suit your needs and only display ads that are relevant to you. As always we respect your privacy and are not collecting any identifiable information through the use of Google’s or any other 3rd party remarketing system.
In addition to using cookies and related technologies as described above, we also may permit certain third party companies to help us tailor advertising that we think may be of interest to users and to collect and use other data about user activities on our Sites and/or Services (e.g., to allow them to tailor ads to third-party services). These companies may deliver ads that might also place cookies and otherwise track user behavior.
